race.Name: Crown Towers Mdn
race.RaceComment: VALBANI (9) finished fourth last start over 1600m at Pinjarra Scarpside and should appreciate dropping back to 1400m today. Rates as one of the main dangers. JUSTAMIDDY (2) could only finish ninth of 14 runner here last start but he did race wide throughout the race. Has a handy draw today and has solid claims in a race which suits. ARTIENNE (10) tried to lead all of the way over 1600m last start but faded out to finish fifth of 10 runners. The 200m less in distance here will suit her and she can gain some well needed form. MOLLY MAGEE (8) resumed from a spell last start and came home well when finishing sixth of 10 runners, she will appreciate the longer distance today. Should improve on that fresh-up run and is a must include in exotic bets.
